description: This DC truck is certainly giving us some good (Reggae) vibes to go along with some good Caribbean grub! Menu items include the classic Jamaican dish, jerk chicken, as well as other delicacies like curry chicken, beef patty, plantains, and much more! If you're in the mood for some rasta treats then channel your inner Bob Marley and join the Reggae Vibes food truck for some delicious eats!
name: Reggae Vibes Food Truck
